  "_comment": "Single source of truth for which companies the pipeline scrapes. To add a company: append one object below with slug, ats, industry, and (for workday only) tenant + site. The pipeline picks up new entries automatically on the next cron run. No Python edits required.",

  "_schema": {
    "slug":     "company identifier — for Greenhouse/Lever this is the URL slug; for Workday it's used as a label",
